The program's lod score matches that calculated using equation 8 of
Cleves/Elston 1997 where family 1 is of type I and the male parent is
informative and family 2 is of type II and the informative parent is female. 
Furthermore, if the pedigree is broken at individual 4 and two separate lod
scores are calculated, the sum of their lod scores equals that of the
combined pedigree.